  "instructions": [
    "in a medium saucepan, heat 1 tsp of olive oil over medium heat.",
    "add sliced ginger and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "add rosemary sprigs and cook for 30 seconds.",
    "add almonds and cook for 2-3 minutes, until lightly toasted.",
    "add maple syrup, salt, black pepper, and cinnamon. stir to combine.",
    "reduce heat to low and simmer for 5-7 minutes, until the mixture has thickened and the almonds are coated in the spice mixture.",
    "remove from heat and let cool completely."
